<plot>The sun rises on Santa Barbara as the dawn patrol hits the waves. Ben checks out the scene. People go to work and school. The virtues and varieties of skateboarding are displayed. Divers encounter a shark. A prophet is self-proclaimed. A young couple take pictures at the beach. Musician's congregate at the Farmer's Market. Chuck Jones shares a few anecdotes. Guys play volleyball on the beach while a young couple fight and surfers ride waves. A man takes pictures of Ben and Bryan. The filmmakers visit a park. A woman is hassled by a cop. The housing and fashion in Santa Barbara are explored; Stacy Peralta and Budgie share anecdotes. Other recreational activities are encountered. The filmmakers return to the Pacific Ocean for a sunset surf session.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?318779</url></doc>
